title: Revamped Underread And Underrated
content:
[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

Welcome to the algorithmically generated under-read and underrated page. Here we aim to amplify works that are likely lower rated than they should be. Works are selected as the most likely to be upvoted by the statistically average wiki voter while remaining under a given threshold.   

These lists should be updated on a monthly basis to represent changes in votes, details on the GoodBoy ranking system can be found on the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/algorithm-curated-recommendations Algorithm Curated Recommendations page].   

Do note that due to a lack of differentiation the generative system tales selected may be in the middle of a series.
